snippet.title: The Silent Neighbor | Full Gameplay
snippet.description:
The Silent Neighbor | Full Gameplay

In the neighborhood you step into, everyone has their secrets... But only your silent neighbor's is deadly. "The Silent Neighbor" is an immersive horror game that combines mystery and suspense. In the depths of a house filled with hidden passages, puzzles, and unexpected perils, you will uncover the dark secrets of your neighbor and strive to stay alive. Solve mind-bending puzzles, navigate through terrifying moments, and dare to confront the cursed past of your silent neighbor. Silence can be deceiving. It is time to face a silent threat in the darkness.
